item.title: List of Falcon 9 and Falcon Heavy launches (2020â€“2022)
item.description: From January 2020, to the end of 2022, Falcon 9 was launched 117 times, all successful, and landed boosters successfully on 111 of those flights. Falcon Heavy was launched once and was successful, including landing of the mission's two side boosters.
